reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect racks for my Ninja AF161 Max
reviews.reviewText: I had to return a set of universal dehydrator racks because they did not fit my air fryer. After reading the reviews, the majority of people commented on only receiving three silicone sleeves to elevate the racks. I took a chance and received these racks within two days. They came with three baskets, six silicone sleeves, and the gripper. My air fryer is 5.5 quarts so it is smaller than the 6 quart average size. I am dehydrating my banana right now. Great purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Basket is fine, The Amazon delivery sucked.
reviews.reviewText: Not the easiest to clean if you are using it as an air fryer basket. The stackable feature is really only good for dehydrating as the gap is too small for practically anything else. Does seem well made. The delivery person left in laying in my neighbors yard down by the street? (watched it on video) maybe because it was raining??...so thanks for that.
